  <div class="column_holder">
    <h1>
      <img alt="JOBS" src="/images/headers/pf_heading/dynamicimage.aspx?text=JOBS" />
    </h1>
    <div class="column_heading">
      <span id="ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_lblTop"><p>GRIN is constantly looking for talented people. All available positions are listed below. Apply via the form or by e-mail.  If you are interested in a position that isn&rsquo;t listed, please send your CV via e-mail to jobs@grin.se.</p></span></div>
    <div class="column_sep">
      <img src="img/jobs/jobs_open_sep.png" alt="Open positions" /></div>
    
    
      <div class="column_content">
        <h1>
          <img alt="Friday 18 January 2008" src="/images/headers/pf_small/dynamicimage.aspx?text=Friday 18 January 2008" />
        </h1>
        <h2>
          <img alt="Animator" src="/images/headers/pf_heading/dynamicimage.aspx?text=Animator" />
        </h2>
        <p>
          <span id="ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_lblJobText"><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%">We at GRIN AB (the developer of titles such as GRAW, GRAW 2, Bionic Commando and Bionic Commando Rearmed) are looking for a talented 3D Animator to take part in our creative team, working on a wide variety of next generation titles. Here you will be members of a strong team specializing in creation of animations that push the concepts of realism to new levels. &nbsp; <o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%">Strong knowledge in either of the major 3D packages is essential, and any experience working with and optimizing motion capture data is advantageous but not a must. Experience with Autodesk Motionbuilder will also be advantageous since this is the 3D animation package used at the studio.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt"><strong><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; color: black; line-height: 115%; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">RESPONSIBILITIES</span></strong><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 36pt; text-indent: -18pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Wingdings"><span>&sect;<span style="font: 7pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%">To create believable high quality animations, export and implement them into the game, and naturally take part in any bug fixing needed.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt 36pt; text-indent: -18pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Wingdings"><span>&sect;<span style="font: 7pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%">Be capable of managing scheduled tasks, and flag potential problems or delays to the respective Lead. <span>&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: black; line-height: 115%; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">EXPECTATIONS</span></strong><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 36pt; text-indent: -18pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Wingdings"><span>&sect;<span style="font: 7pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%">Strong knowledge in any major 3D animation package is essential. Experience with Autodesk Motionbuilder would be advantageous.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 36pt; text-indent: -18pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Wingdings"><span>&sect;<span style="font: 7pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%">As no direct experience with animation for games is expected having worked on published titles is naturally advantageous, as is any knowledge implementing key-framed animation into any game engine.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 36pt; text-indent: -18pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Wingdings"><span>&sect;<span style="font: 7pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%">Must be able to take direction and learn from the creative team.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 36pt; text-indent: -18pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Wingdings"><span>&sect;<span style="font: 7pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%">The ability to communicate with the team effectively either through storyboards, spoken word and/or physically.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><strong><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; color: black; line-height: 115%; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">DEMO REEL REQUIREMENTS</span></strong><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; color: black; line-height: 115%"><br />
</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%">Have a Demo reel </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; color: black; line-height: 115%">(online, CD or DVD format) </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%">demonstrating a great understanding of all the essential animation concepts showing the ability to convey emotion through movement. <o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; color: black; line-height: 115%">Applicants must provide demo reel/CD/DVD or website address to be considered for any animation position.</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%"><br />
<br />
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt"><strong><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10pt; color: black; line-height: 115%; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Positions in Stockholm and&nbsp;Gothenburg.</span></strong></p></span></p>
      </div>
      <div class="column_nav">
        <span class="column_nav_cat">Contact</span>
        <p>
          Please send your application through the online form below, or by regular mail to
          our physical adress. If you prefer to send your application by email click
          <a href="&#109;&#97;&#105;&#108;&#116;&#111;&#58;&#97;&#110;&#105;&#109;&#97;&#116;&#105;&#111;&#110;&#64;&#103;&#114;&#105;&#110;&#46;&#115;&#101;">here</a>.</p>
      </div>
